WEBVTT

00:00.774 --> 00:02.502
<i>Previously on</i>
Beauty & the Beast...

00:02.503 --> 00:04.507
You okay, buddy? Who's he?

00:04.508 --> 00:06.209
Uh, I don't know.
A prisoner.

00:09.913 --> 00:12.273
Honestly, it helps more to know
that we stopped these heists

00:12.282 --> 00:14.049
and we got Barnes.

00:14.084 --> 00:16.352
Apparently the ID on that
kidnapper is Frank Darnell.

00:16.386 --> 00:17.953
This guy was just a front man

00:17.988 --> 00:19.688
for whoever
Tony Barnes really is.

00:19.723 --> 00:20.723
Where's the guy
in the cell?

00:20.757 --> 00:22.424
Dana.
Oh, my God, Sam.

00:22.458 --> 00:23.926
<i>We found bone chips.</i>

00:23.960 --> 00:26.461
Darnell has been burning bodies
underneath Sam's cell.

00:26.496 --> 00:27.930
<i>And when I asked him about it,</i>

00:27.964 --> 00:29.197
he denied knowing anything.

00:29.232 --> 00:30.633
Let him think
that his plan is working.

00:30.667 --> 00:32.134
Con the con man.

00:32.168 --> 00:34.048
This con is to make us think
you're the bad guy.

00:34.070 --> 00:35.770
I think we need to let
this thing go off.

00:35.804 --> 00:37.305
If I die,
then the bad guy is gone.

00:37.340 --> 00:39.608
Case closed. He'll think
that you guys will stop

00:39.642 --> 00:41.309
<i>investigating</i>
<i>and he won't have to kill you.</i>

00:43.613 --> 00:44.712
Catherine,
what are you doing here?

00:44.747 --> 00:45.913
I wasn't going to leave you.

